Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.22,0:12:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你在幹什麼呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.26,0:12:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,祈禱?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.16,0:12:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,是追悼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.56,0:12:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,追悼?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.68,0:12:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,快看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.40,0:12:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,他正頂著太陽往前走
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.96,0:12:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,他已經不行了  出局了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.40,0:12:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,這就是規則
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.72,0:13:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,小妹妹…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.34,0:13:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你和姐姐我之前見過面來著?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.24,0:13:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,是錯覺嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.98,0:13:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.02,0:13:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,注意太陽光
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.92,0:13:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.44,0:13:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,媽媽來了  萌香
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.16,0:13:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,那我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.52,0:13:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.70,0:13:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,一直等著媽媽  真乖
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.36,0:13:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,今晚想吃什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.12,0:13:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我想想…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.02,0:13:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,昨晚吃的是咖哩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.00,0:13:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,今天就吃漢堡肉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.72,0:13:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,茶泡飯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.80,0:13:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我家萌香真是老成
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.62,0:13:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了  萌香?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.76,0:13:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,媽媽  你出局了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.94,0:13:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,哦  原來是不能走出影子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.04,0:13:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  這就是規則
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.84,0:14:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,那媽媽還真得注意了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.42,0:14:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.62,0:14:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,對了  萌香
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.24,0:14:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,要送給爺爺的禮物  好好地帶在身上了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.66,0:14:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  帶著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.36,0:14:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,圓石頭
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.24,0:14:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.18,0:14:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我還畫了幅爺爺
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.16,0:14:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn萝莉体 第二版\fs60\bord0\shad0\c&H090517&\frz5.048\pos(933,199.716)}我愛    爺爺
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.70,0:14:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,哦  畫得真好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.60,0:14:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,爺爺肯定會很高興的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.22,0:14:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,話說回來  萌香你真會畫畫
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.96,0:14:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,長大了當畫家?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.96,0:14:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,美姬社
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.00,0:14:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,萌香長大了要美姬社!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.14,0:14:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,美姬社?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.24,0:14:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,啊  是美術社?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.60,0:14:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.18,0:14:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,說起來  爺爺說他前些日子還是美術社的顧問老師來著…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.34,0:14:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,爺爺也美術社?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.22,0:14:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,讓他給你講講吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.60,0:14:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.44,0:14:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,萌香…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.46,0:14:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,出局了
